Content: In the clinical trials described in the book they administered in by IV.  DMT is everywhere, in plants and animals.  Synthesizing it is difficult though.  Our pineal gland, a vestigial third eye located in the center of our brain is thought to release spurts of DMT during REM sleep, birth and near death experiences.  One of the theories is that it allows for the soul to enter/exit the body which is why we see it released in quantity during birth and near death experiences.
